{"tid":368640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[求推介] 韓國菜/川菜","createTime":"2017-08-21T16:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T08:55:10.000Z","uid":109294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8334e78c675b9abdf6935834d591fe97db633e72","tid":368640,"uid":109294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"1）2個人食<br />\n2）最好係觀塘/油尖/深水埗區。如果好特別既話其他區都可以考慮。<br />\n3）平日夜晚9點半食<br />\n4）價錢不拘，好吃便可。如果有啲特色野食既話就最好。<br />\n<br />\n求咁多連登巴絲推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cf925b890d9ce046171fabbeeae664fbb38a15","tid":368640,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"三個地方我都好熟 留名聽日答你 <br />\n幾時食？"},{"pid":"ddb09f001bb9e5279cb5b6722db99967afcc549d","tid":368640,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"留名 我都想食呢2樣！！！！！！"},{"pid":"57e4a1e2b6b83d9ceb2685937ab14d0d26efd298","tid":368640,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:28:01.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀 寶勒巷 元豐園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚餐唔錯<br />\n傳統韓國菜<br />\n個人比較建議午餐，2個人百零蚊埋單，仲有九百幾樣前菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a9e0cfcdecb6ee54da0aef99ad23f394902b1","tid":368640,"uid":109294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T22:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個地方我都好熟 留名聽日答你 <br />\n幾時食？</blockquote><br />\n今晚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ae3915a5badf23ac25fc8d9c6181d00e25fd96","tid":368640,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三個地方我都好熟 留名聽日答你 <br />\n幾時食？</blockquote><br />\n今晚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多選擇 我都要諗諗"},{"pid":"015bf9f7fd37f4efc010bd508f3d03c1b67a5383","tid":368640,"uid":109294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三個地方我都好熟 留名聽日答你 <br />\n幾時食？</blockquote><br />\n今晚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多選擇 我都要諗諗</blockquote><br />\n揀幾間你食過最正既囉"},{"pid":"ae25cb9b6830ff179a8f911954cc34fc32da88e8","tid":368640,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1）2個人食<br />\n2）最好係觀塘/油尖/深水埗區。如果好特別既話其他區都可以考慮。<br />\n3）平日夜晚9點半食<br />\n4）價錢不拘，好吃便可。如果有啲特色野食既話就最好。<br />\n<br />\n求咁多連登巴絲推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n川菜去三希樓 中環"},{"pid":"83db1650e651b4c4ac860eaa8f16ac94777ad227","tid":368640,"uid":611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三個地方我都好熟 留名聽日答你 <br />\n幾時食？</blockquote><br />\n今晚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多選擇 我都要諗諗</blockquote><br />\n揀幾間你食過最正既囉</blockquote><br />\n唔記得件事 😂<br />\n不如試下尖沙咀間大阪烤肉 啲野唔錯 又幾有氣氛<br />\n同埋 旺角黑布街有間Bar restaurant 叫De Luna <br />\n仲有 Jordon 有間叫HaruHaru 座位小小 啲野幾得<br />\n中菜 大角咀 有間叫老掌櫃 食東北菜 啲野幾特色架<br />\n深水埗 食小炒可以去食 高高酒家 我食過晒深水埗長沙灣所有小炒 呢家第一 無得傾<br />\n德國菜可以去朗豪坊頂樓果度有間食德國野唔錯 都幾正宗 <br />\n韓燒去炑八啦 都係不二之選 係太子有分店 有韓牛食"},{"pid":"738845110c9018968bb08c811ac1b5238448fca7","tid":368640,"uid":611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"補充小小 想食打邊爐去深水埗 大煲皇 成深水埗散叫黎講 我覺得佢最好食 <br />\n想食蒸氣鍋 就試下黃金樓上果間潮福 人小小 唔洗去旺角同人逼 三舊幾一位任食 啲食物質素真心唔錯<br />\n食雞煲烤魚 香港無一間正宗同好食 雞煲最好食就係滿堂紅 油麻地同深水埗有分店 烤魚真係要上大陸食探魚 香港我食過幾十間想搵返果個味道都搵唔到"},{"pid":"81a2155e533